TextEng: Where has Desther gone?
Don't play games! You are in league with him!
Fenthick, what have you done?
Aribeth is waiting for you. Waiting for an explanation.
Text: 아리베스가 기다리고 있어요. 설명을 기다리고 있죠.

TextEng: Why me not kill you right now?!
Text: 왜 지금 당장 너 안 죽여?!

TextEng: We'll let a court decide that. Or a mob.
Text: 그건 법정이 판단하게 두죠. 아니면 군중에게.

TextEng: What you do, Fenthick?
Bah! You in league with him!
Where Desther go?
A court decide that stuff. Or maybe a mob.
Why shouldn't I kill you right now?!
Text: 왜 지금 당장 당신을 죽이면 안 되지?!

TextEng: Do you know who he is working for?
You maybe know who Desther work for?
Where is he now?
Where he now?
Why didn't he want us to have the cure?
Text: 왜 우리가 치료약을 갖는 걸 원하지 않았죠?

TextEng: Why he not want us to get cure?
Text: 왜 우리 치료제 갖는 거 싫어했어?

TextEng: I must find Desther. What do you intend to do?
Text: 난 데스터를 찾아야 합니다. 어떻게 할 생각이죠?

TextEng: Me go find Desther. What you gonna do, hmm?
Text: 나 데스터 찾으러 가. 너는 뭐 할 거야, 흠?

TextEng: Aribeth waits for your reasons. She gots questions.
Text: 아리베스가 이유 묻고 기다려. 물어볼 게 많아.

TextEng: What are these Old Ones?
Desther spread the plague? How?
Desther spread plague? When he do that?
But what initially caused the plague? What started it?
Text: 하지만 역병은 처음에 왜 생긴 거죠? 무엇이 시작한 겁니까?

TextEng: Okay, but what first started the plague stuff?
Text: 좋아, 그런데 처음엔 뭐가 이 역병을 시작했어?

TextEng: Old Ones? What they?
Let's go back to my previous questions.
Back to other questions, okay?
He say what "People of the Eye" supposed to do?
Text: 그가 "눈동자 교단"이 뭐 해야 한다고 말했어?

TextEng: Has he shed any light on the purpose of the "People of the Eye?"
Text: 눈동자 교단의 목적에 대해 뭔가 밝혀낸 게 있나요?
